        " فَقَالَ \"كُلْ وَ قِرَّ وَ اِسْتَقِرَّ حَتَّى يَكُونَ مَا يَكُونُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4179 - Al-Halabi asked him about the slaughtered animal of the Murji'ite and the Haruri. Imam (as) said: \"Eat, and be at ease and settled until whatever is to happen occurs.\""
        ]
